data.text:
Food

The only thing better than the energetic and inviting atmosphere at Hooters is our mouth-watering food. From appetizers and fresh salads to burgers and our World-Famous wings, we have a lineup of delicious menu options sure to satisfy any taste.

* Please check with your local Hooters as some menu items might be unavailable at this time.*

Order online

Onion Rings

Twelve onion rings cooked to a golden brown and then served with remoulade and ranch dressing

Curly Fries

add nacho cheese sauce

Fried Pickles

Handmade to order and served with our signature tangy dipping sauce

Chili Cheese Fries

Served with jalapeños

Buffalo Shrimp

10/20 in choice of wing sauce

Quesadillas

Chicken, Steak or Cheese

Cheese Sticks

Fried mozzarella cheese with marinara sauce. Enough said.

Lots a Tots

Tater tots covered with bacon, cheese, sour cream and chives

Burger Sliders (4)

Fresh ground beef topped with cheese, mustard, pickles.

Served with fries.

Buffalo Chicken Sliders (4)

Buffalo chicken tossed with your choice of wing sauce,

topped with pickles and served with your choice bleu cheese or ranch and fries

Buffalo Chicken Dip

Shredded chicken mixed in with a variety of cheeses served with ranch or blue cheese dressing, served with spiced tortilla chips.

Beer Cheese & Pretzels

A creamy blend of cheese infused with stout beer and served with salted Bavarian pretzels.

Tex Mex Nachos

Fresh chips loaded with gooey cheese and chili, piled high with fresh quacamole, lettuce, fresh pico de gallo, jalapenos, sour cream and our avocado ranch.

Smothered Chicken Sandwich

Topped with sauteed onions, green peppers and muchrooms. Smothered in melted provolone cheese and served on a toasted brioche bun.

Grilled Chicken Sandwich

Grilled chicken with lettuce and tomato served on a toasted brioche bun.

Buffalo Chicken Sandwich

Everything you love about our wings, but in a sandwich.

Hand-breaded chicken breast tossed in your favorite wing

sauce, and served on a toasted brioche bun.

Grilled Mahi Sandwich

Grilled Mahi with lettuce and tomato served on a toasted brioche bun. Also available bronzed.

Philly Cheese

A sandwich with attitude. Steak or chicken topped with sautéed

onions, green peppers, mushrooms and provolone cheese and

served on a hoagie roll.

Buffalo Chicken Wrap

Tossed in your favorite wing sauce

Buffalo Chicken Tacos

Is there anything Buffalo chicken can’t do? Grilled or crispy

chicken tossed in your favorite wing sauce, topped with cabbage,

pico de gallo and your choice of ranch or bleu cheese inside flour tortillas.

Gourmet Hot Dog Platter

Adult Grilled Cheese
